flowchart LR
    Run["npm run test:evidence"] --> Node["执行全部 Node 测试"]
    Run --> UI["执行 Chromium UI 测试"]
    Node --> Record["创建永久测试批次"]
    UI --> Record
    Record --> Raw["node.log / ui.log"]
    Record --> Report["result.md / metadata.json / test-cases.json"]
    Record --> Browser["playwright-report / test-results"]
    Raw --> Manifest["evidence-manifest.json + checksums.sha256"]
    Report --> Manifest
    Browser --> Manifest
    Manifest --> Verify["test:evidence:verify 校验缺失、新增和篡改"]
    Record --> List["test:evidence:list 查询历史批次"]
